-----> DEPENDENCIES ?

Required packages:

    * GTK+ - The GIMP Toolkit library, version >= 2.12
    * LibXML 2 library 

Optional packages:

    * Libnotify library, version >= 0.4.4
    * Libgtkhtml2 library, version >= 2.2.0
    * Libical library, version >= 0.33
    * Libtar library, version >= 1.2.10
    * Libgringotts library, version >= 1.2.1 


